io.parallec.core.resources

Class HttpClientStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.parallec.core.resources.HttpClientStore

  • public class HttpClientStore
extends java.lang.Object
    this stores a pair of default embedded fast/slow AsyncHttpClient, and another pair of customized fast/slow AsyncHttpClient. By default the pair of customized ones are just references (duplicates of) the embedded ones. For each Parallel Task, will by default load the Embed-fast client in AsyncHttpClientStore unless you load your specific async http client. You may call setHttpClientTypeCurrentDefault(HttpClientType) to change the default one (default one is the embedded fast)
    Author:
    Yuanteng (Jeff) Pei
